title: Nordo in for PA #92Noon! Micheletti/Leber/Miller
description: It's a hockey heavy #92Noon as Nordo fills in for PA! Pat Micheletti talks Wild and more, former Beyond The Pond co-host and Miracle star Nate Miller talks about the 40th anniversary of the Miracle on Ice, and Ben Leber makes his regular appearance to talk new NFL rules and to preview the combine!
